            "children": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "Stanford University has made significant strides in sustainability, implementing comprehensive programs to reduce its environmental footprint and serve as a model for other institutions. The university's "
                },
                {
                    "type": "tag",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "value": "Stanford Energy System Innovations"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": " project has transformed the campus energy infrastructure, reducing greenhouse gas emissions by 68% and saving millions of dollars annually."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "tag",
            "tag": "p",
            "children": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "Beyond energy, Stanford's sustainability efforts encompass water conservation, waste reduction, and sustainable transportation. The university has achieved "
                },
                {
                    "type": "tag",
                    "tag": "em",
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "value": "zero waste"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": " status and continues to innovate in sustainable practices that can be replicated globally."
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
    "infoBox": {
        "title": "Environmental Impact",
        "content": [
            {
                "type": "tag",
                "tag": "p",
                "children": [
